<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 09:13:07 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美团第四季度营收超出预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/meituan-beats-q4-revenue-expectations-2024-03-22/</link><description>中国食品配送巨头美团点评周五公布，季度收入增长 22.6%，超出预期，无视中国经济放缓的影响。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 08:55:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/meituan-beats-q4-revenue-expectations-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>在大型中国芯片展上，企业纷纷呼吁购买国产芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/major-china-chip-fair-firms-ramp-up-call-buy-domestic-2024-03-22/</link><description>中国半导体相关公司本周在该国最大的芯片行业展会之一上竭尽全力推销国内采购，呼应了北京方面为面临日益加剧的地缘政治压力的行业提供支持的呼吁。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 08:52:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/major-china-chip-fair-firms-ramp-up-call-buy-domestic-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，英国法律总局搁置中国营业执照计划并裁员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/uks-legal-general-shelves-china-business-licence-plan-cuts-headcount-sources-say-2024-03-22/</link><description>两位消息人士称，英国保险公司和资产管理公司 Legal &amp;amp; General 搁置了获得中国营业执照的计划，并将境内员工人数减少了一半以上，加入了在不确定的市场中缩减规模的全球金融公司名单。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 06:23:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/uks-legal-general-shelves-china-business-licence-plan-cuts-headcount-sources-say-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚、英国呼吁中国支持香港、南海和俄罗斯</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/australia-britain-warn-potentially-devastating-consequences-israeli-operation-2024-03-22/</link><description>周五，在伦敦和堪培拉深化安全关系的会议后，澳大利亚和英国批评中国在香港、南海的行动以及对俄罗斯的支持。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 06:16:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/australia-britain-warn-potentially-devastating-consequences-israeli-operation-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，中国正在审查普华永道在恒大 780 亿美元欺诈案中所扮演的角色</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-scrutinises-pwc-role-78-bln-evergrande-fraud-case-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-03-22/</link><description>据彭博社周五报道，在中国恒大集团被指控欺诈 780 亿美元后，中国当局正在审查普华永道 (PwC) 在该集团会计实践中所扮演的角色。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 05:48:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-scrutinises-pwc-role-78-bln-evergrande-fraud-case-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，英国法律总局搁置中国营业执照计划并裁员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/uks-legal-general-shelves-china-business-license-plan-cuts-headcount-sources-say-2024-03-22/</link><description>两位消息人士称，英国保险公司和资产管理公司 Legal &amp;amp; General 搁置了获得中国营业执照的计划，并将境内员工人数减少了一半以上，加入了在不确定的市场中缩减规模的全球金融公司名单。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 04:32:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/uks-legal-general-shelves-china-business-license-plan-cuts-headcount-sources-say-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国特使表示，俄罗斯和乌克兰认为危机最终通过谈判解决</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-ukraine-see-crisis-eventually-resolved-through-talks-chinas-special-envoy-2024-03-22/</link><description>中国欧亚事务特使周五表示，俄罗斯和乌克兰都相信冲突将通过谈判结束，尽管交战国对和谈前景的看法截然不同，而且立场坚定。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 03:35:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-ukraine-see-crisis-eventually-resolved-through-talks-chinas-special-envoy-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>人民币跌至四个月低点，国有银行介入</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/china-yuan-drops-four-month-low-state-banks-step-2024-03-22/</link><description>周五，人民币兑美元汇率跌至四个月低点，突破关键门槛，促使国有银行介入捍卫人民币。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 03:30:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/china-yuan-drops-four-month-low-state-banks-step-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国的悲观情绪让亚洲降息的欢呼失去了活力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-22/</link><description>人民币周五大幅下跌，中国股市下滑，拖累亚洲市场普遍下跌，并抑制了瑞士意外降息引发的股市上涨，投资者押注谁将放松政策。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 02:25:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>瑞士降息暗示潜在利率差距，美元每周上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steadfast-investors-seek-carry-2024-03-22/</link><description>美元周五将连续第二周大幅上涨，即使日本加息也无法阻止其前进步伐，而瑞士的意外降息凸显了美联储与全球同行在利率设置上的差距。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 01:20:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steadfast-investors-seek-carry-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>朝中社称，朝鲜派遣代表团访问中国、越南、老挝</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-sends-delegation-china-vietnam-laos-kcna-says-2024-03-21/</link><description>官方媒体朝中社周五表示，朝鲜已向中国、越南和老挝派遣了一个代表团，这个孤立的国家在 COVID-19 封锁后扩大了外交接触。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 23:11:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-sends-delegation-china-vietnam-laos-kcna-says-2024-03-21/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟和美国讨论如何解决中国作为俄罗斯商品渠道的角色</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/eu-us-discussed-how-address-chinas-role-conduit-goods-russia-2024-03-21/</link><description>欧盟制裁协调员周四表示，欧盟及其盟国正在考虑采取措施解决中国出口可能帮助俄罗斯军方的商品问题，包括实施进一步制裁。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 22:41:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/eu-us-discussed-how-address-chinas-role-conduit-goods-russia-2024-03-21/</guid></item><item><title>官员称中国中芯国际可能违反美国出口限制生产华为芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-smic-may-have-violated-us-export-curbs-make-huawei-chip-official-2024-03-21/</link><description>美国商务部一位高级官员在周四的国会听证会上表示，拜登政府表示，中国最大的芯片制造商中芯国际生产为华为 Mate 60 Pro 手机供电的芯片可能违反了美国的出口规定，但仍在评估情况。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 15:17:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-smic-may-have-violated-us-export-curbs-make-huawei-chip-official-2024-03-21/</guid></item><item><title>BAE 赢得 AUKUS 潜艇项目，澳大利亚拨款数十亿美元建设海军基础设施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/australia-earmarks-billions-naval-infrastructure-bae-wins-aukus-submarine-work-2024-03-21/</link><description>澳大利亚周四表示，根据 AUKUS 安全协议，将斥资数十亿美元在国内和英国建造核动力潜艇的码头、造船厂和工厂，并指定英国 BAE Systems 帮助建造这些潜艇。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 11:33:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/australia-earmarks-billions-naval-infrastructure-bae-wins-aukus-submarine-work-2024-03-21/</guid></item><item><title>苹果库克在上海开设新店，迎合中国销量下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apples-ceo-cook-opens-new-store-shanghai-2024-03-21/</link><description>苹果公司首席执行官蒂姆·库克周四在上海开设了最新的苹果店，在一大群人面前开业，其中一些人连夜排队。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 11:19:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apples-ceo-cook-opens-new-store-shanghai-2024-03-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>